  • Class
    Description
    ApiException
    API exceptions with developer-friendly messages.
    Location
    Contains the sensor's location information.
    MessageHandler
    Handles the SignalQuest Transport Protocol message parsing for SignalQuest sensors.
    MessageHandler.MessageReceiver
    Receives messages, parsed from sensor data, with MessageHandler.parse(byte[]).
    NtripParser
    Parses the NTRIP authorization and RTCM messages.
    NtripParser.AuthorizationFailure
    Indicates an NTRIP authorization failure.
    NtripParser.RtcmReceiver
    Receives RTCM messages, parsed with NtripParser.parseRtcm(byte[]), that can be written to a SitePoint RTCM characteristic.
    ScanStatus
    Contains the BLE scanning information.
    Status
    Contains the sensor status information.
